page.title: 06A Traffic Survey.
page.content:
TOTAL NUMBER OF VEHICLES USING EACH OF THE FIVE MAIN STREETS OF WHITCHURCH DURING THE PERIOD 14.00HRS_I4.30HRS ON WEDNESDAY 19 JUNE I985.
NEWBURY STREET 106 LONDON STREET 154 WINCHESTER STREET 109 CHURCH STREET 163 BELL STREET 64
The heaviest amounts of traffic were along the roads going to Basingstoke and Andover.When we talked about which roads would be the busiest we thought that London Street and Church Street wpuld be the busiest and our results proved that we had thought correctly.
